HEADWORD: Necropolis
<hw>Ne*crop"o*lis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Necropolises</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <?/;
<grk>nekro`s</grk> a dead body, adj., dead + <?/ city.]</ety> <def>A
